### Hadith 4:271

*Narrated Jabir:*

The Prophet said, "Who is ready to kill Ka'b bin Ashraf (i.e. a Jew)."
Muhammad bin Maslama replied, "Do you like me to kill him?" The Prophet
replied in the affirmative. Muhammad bin Maslama said, "Then allow me to
say what I like." The Prophet replied, "I do (i.e. allow you)."

